column5: YTEN They are absolutely the final presenter at Ladenburg Curious as to whether anyone will be in the audience for their presentation Not that it matters This conference is hardly make or break and seems obligatory in that Ladenburg is by far and away the best analyst covering these guys In fact the other two guys who call in sound like Sacha Baron Cohen punking the company Attendance feels compulsory as a thank you to the guy at Ladenburg who is doing admirable work on the company The big news will have to be sometime in June when announce a joint partnership a buy out or heaven for bid yet another capital raise
